'''梨熟'''是[[朝鮮半島|朝鮮]]傳統甜品[[花菜_(甜品)|花菜]]的一種，以[[沙梨|沙梨]]、[[花椒|花椒]]、[[薑|薑]]、[[蜂蜜|蜂蜜]]或[[糖|糖]]為材料，加[[水|水]]煮熟而成<ref>[http://www.clickkorea.org/Food/foodguide_view.asp?menubar=4&page=&sendpage=foodSearchList_2.asp&idx=376 Click Korea: Access to Korean Arts & Culture<!-- Bot generated title -->] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110719021840/http://www.clickkorea.org/Food/foodguide_view.asp?menubar=4&page=&sendpage=foodSearchList_2.asp&idx=376 |date=2011-07-19 }}</ref>，這也是梨熟的名稱由來<ref name="encyber">{{cite web|url=http://www.encyber.com/search_w/ctdetail.php?masterno=72150&contentno=72150 |title=梨熟 (배숙) |publisher=[[斗山世界大百科事典|斗山世界大百科事典]] |accessdate=2008-05-19 |language=ko }}{{dead link|date=六月 2017 |bot=InternetArchiveBot }}</ref>。梨熟本為[[朝鮮宮廷料理|朝鮮宮廷料理]]，直至[[二十世紀|二十世紀]]中期才流傳到民間<ref name="encyber" />。把梨子去皮後切片或以全梨去煮皆可<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.digitalorganic.net/bbs/board.php?bo_table=welbeing&wr_id=3 |title=잡지 > 참살이 > 배숙<!-- Bot generated title --> |accessdate=2008-12-29 |archive-date=2011-07-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110723102605/http://www.digitalorganic.net/bbs/board.php?bo_table=welbeing&wr_id=3 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。煮之前要在每片梨上嵌入三至五顆花椒<ref name="food in Korea">{{cite web |url=http://www.foodinkorea.org/eng_food/foodculture/foodculture1_6_b.jsp |title=Baesuk (Cooked Pear) |publisher=Korea Agro-Fisheries Trade Corporation |accessdate=2008-05-19 |language=en |archive-date=2008-04-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080423235811/http://www.foodinkorea.org/eng_food/foodculture/foodculture1_6_b.jsp |dead-url=no }}</ref>。如以全梨製作，多會選用果肉較硬、味較酸的[[秋子梨|秋子梨]]（Pyrus ussuriensis），成品稱為'''香雪膏'''（{{lang|ko|향설고}}、{{lang|ko|香雪膏}}）<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.sanrimji.com/pdf/2004/11/200411086(1).pdf |title=서울의 희귀종 문배나무 기준 표본목 |language=ko |accessdate=2008-06-16 |author=Ju Jinsun (주진순) |publisher=National Forestry Cooperatives Federation |archive-date=2005-05-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20050524053402/http://www.sanrimji.com/pdf/2004/11/200411086(1).pdf |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://alldic.empas.com/search/alldic.html?category=A&q=%C7%E2%BC%B3%B0%ED&x=11&y=6&wi=51&po=Y&wv=51&ob=1&ds=44 |title=香雪膏 |publisher=[[Empas|Empas Korean Dictionary]] |language=ko |accessdate=2008-06-16}}</ref>。梨熟通常在夏季或[[朝鮮秋夕|中秋節]]食用<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.kado.net/news/articleView.html?idxno=278346 |title=::: 강원도민일보 :::<!-- Bot generated title --> |accessdate=2008-12-29 |archive-date=2011-10-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111004035909/http://www.kado.net/news/articleView.html?idxno=278346 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://healthcare.evercare.co.kr/service_menu/webzine/wz_02_view.jsp?p_seq=198&p_subject=0004 |title=에버케어 헬스케어<!-- Bot generated title --> |accessdate=2008-12-29 |archive-date=2012-06-30 |archive-url=https://archive.today/20120630042547/http://healthcare.evercare.co.kr/service_menu/webzine/wz_02_view.jsp?p_seq=198&p_subject=0004 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

由於梨熟和另一種朝鮮傳統甜品[[水正果|水正果]]（{{lang|ko|수정과}}、{{lang|ko|水正果}}）的製法相似，因此也稱為'''梨水正果'''（{{lang|ko|배수정과}}，{{lang|ko|배}}為固有詞）<ref name="encyber" />。由於梨熟味道清甜且製法簡單，在[[韓國|韓國]]很受歡迎<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.invil.org/english/speciality/fruit/pear/contents.jsp?con_no=854034&page_no=1 |title=Naju Pear |publisher=Information Newwork Village |accessdate=2008-05-19 |language=en |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110718112215/http://www.invil.org/english/speciality/fruit/pear/contents.jsp?con_no=854034&page_no=1 |archivedate=2011-07-18 }}</ref>，除了作為[[甜品|甜品]]外，也有[[食療|食療]]功用<ref name="傷風">[http://huryoungman.co.kr/sik/health/2769 환절기 감기, 건강차로 이겨내자<!-- Bot generated title -->] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080804060357/http://www.huryoungman.co.kr/sik/health/2769 |date=2008-08-04 }}</ref><ref name="冰高麗蔘精茶梨熟">{{Cite web |url=http://www.nownews.com/2006/12/14/11015-2026256.htm |title=冰高麗蔘精茶梨熟 |accessdate=2008-12-29 |archive-date=2013-08-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130818024736/http://www.nownews.com/2006/12/14/11015-2026256.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==製作方法==
把切片的梨子放入加有薑片、糖或蜂蜜的熱水裡以中火煮<ref name="encyber" />，煮熟後拿開薑片，然後把梨和水一同舀進[[碗|碗]]裡，再灑上[[松子|松子]]，亦可再加入[[柚子|柚子]]汁食用<ref name="encyKorea">{{cite web |url=http://100.empas.com/dicsearch/pentry.html?s=K&i=242441&v=46 |title=Baesuk (배숙) |publisher=[[Empas|Empas]] / [[EncyKorea|EncyKorea]] |accessdate=2008-05-19 |language=ko |archive-date=2007-03-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070321143002/http://100.empas.com/dicsearch/pentry.html?s=K |dead-url=no }}</ref>，若冷吃的話則在拿開薑片後把梨和水放進[[冰箱|冰箱]]內或以[[冰|冰]]塊鎮涼，吃前才加松子。
==功效==
{{ctm}}
梨熟可作[[藥膳|藥膳]]。梨子能[[利尿|利尿]]，亦可緩和[[胃潰瘍|胃潰瘍]]、[[便秘|便秘]]，對[[膽|膽]]、[[解熱|解熱]]、[[咳嗽|咳嗽]]等方面具有顯著療效，而梨為強[[鹼性|鹼性]]食品，可使[[血液|血液]]維持中性，亦可作日常保健和預防成人病。溫性的生薑可促進血液循環，使手腳和身體保持溫暖，並且促進胃腸作用，有利於消化和預防[[腹痛|腹痛]]、[[泄瀉|腹泄病]]，生薑煮茶飲用在[[冬季|冬季]]亦可有效預防[[感冒|感冒]]<ref name="冰高麗蔘精茶梨熟" />，對[[普通感冒|普通感冒]]亦有一定療效<ref name="傷風" />。

